    "subject": "Disguised enemy name is shown inconsistently",
    "description": "This has been a bothering issue since quite long time but now I managed to make a ticket about it. In the demo, the player on the left hand side is an enemy covert op and the player on the right side is your friend. When you move your mouse from right to left over the enemy in disguise, you will see how the name disappears very fast from the HUD. But when you move your mouse from left to right, it shows it like it would show on the friendly player, the name disappears normally.\r\n\r\nIn the demo you can also see another bug related to demo playback when you look at the fireteam on the top left corner.\r\n\r\nThere's an demo attached, watch and see.\r\n\r\n-*S",
